          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What should I expect with resin preservation?",
            "answer": "<p>Natural characteristics may include:</p><ul><li>Small air bubbles, especially near charms or brooches</li><li>Color changes (whites may yellow, reds may darken)</li><li>Minor grooves or surface variations</li><li>Silica gel beads</li><li>Flyaway flower fibers</li><li>Transparency or color shifts with fabric or lace</li></ul><p></p><p>These are normal and part of handcrafted resin work.</p>"
          }
        }
